File Permissions
chmod - Change file permissions

bash

Verify

Open In Editor
Edit
Copy code
chmod 755 script.sh  # Owner can read/write/execute; others can read/execute
chown - Change file owner and group

bash

Verify

Open In Editor
Edit
Copy code
chown user:group file.txt
